                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "As seen in bug 259480 comment #12, mailnews.display.show_all_body_parts_menu=true and View/Mesage Body As/All Body Parts(introduced by bug 602718) is efective in your case.\n", 
